"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1927359-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-time-tv-channel\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The greatest show on earth, theOlympic Games,bursts into life today with what is sure to be a memorable opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The greatest show\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 17}, {\"ngram\": \"earth\", \"from\": 21, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Games\", \"from\": 28, \"to\": 44}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 57, \"to\": 61}, {\"ngram\": \"a memorable opening ceremony\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a break with tradition, the ceremony will not take place in the Games' athletics stadium, the Stade de France, but along a 6km stretch of the River Seine.\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 134}, {\"ngram\": \"tradition\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 149}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 163}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 183}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' athletics stadium\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6km stretch\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will begin at Austerlitz bridge and end among the gardens, fountains and palaces in the shadow of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 300, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"score\": 0.9929157122778688, \"rank\": 0.007134832867991177, \"text\": \"Austerlitz\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gardens\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"fountains\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"palaces\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"the shadow\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will feature 100 boats carrying more than 10,000 athletes, plus dignitaries, which will sail past Paris' iconic landmarks, including Notre Dame cathedral.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999652118, \"rank\": 3.487726267941792e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100 boats\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 10,000 athletes\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"dignitaries\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre Dame cathedral\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as transporting the athletes in the parade, the boats will also be used in the artistic part of the ceremony, which will showcase the history and culture of Paris and France.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999652118, \"rank\": 3.487726267941792e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9844064232486098, \"rank\": 0.008838246716280992, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"the parade\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"the boats\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"the artistic part\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 677}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other details, like the identity of performers, are being kept secret, but there are sure to be some surprise appearances.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other details\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"the identity\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"some surprise appearances\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Express Sportbrings you all the vital details about watching the ceremony, including start time and TV channel\\u2026 Festivities are due to commence at 7.30pm local time (6.30pm in the UK).\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999565085787665, \"rank\": 4.1379061084526995e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"TV channel\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"Festivities\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"commence\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"7.30pm local time\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is expected to last around four hours with the final stages taking place as the sun sets across Paris.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999652118, \"rank\": 3.487726267941792e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around four hours\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"the final stages\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the sun\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time of writing, the weather forecast looks mixed - with a risk of thunder showers in the evening.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"writing\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather forecast\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"a risk\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"thunder showers\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony will be broadcast onBBCOne, with coverage getting underway at 5.45pm.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ceremony\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"coverage\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"5.45pm\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The broadcast is due to conclude at 10pm but could well run over.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The broadcast\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also watch the ceremony via iPlayer and follow it on BBC Radio 5 Live.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbp